There have been many reports of Yuri's sightings.[l][r]
Perhaps it was only natural, considering their appearance. But, given the amount of information, we were unable to obtain any clues as to their movements or destination.[l][r]
This is especially true for Chito. Even school officials say that the last time they saw her was more than two months before her disappearance.[l][r]
The university had sent two notices of withdrawal for both of them, and the entire amount had been withdrawn from their bank accounts. The withdrawals were undoubtedly made by them. In other words, they had planned it thoroughly. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

