[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
The last person to see them in the country was an airport employee. The flight they boarded was bound for Hong Kong. It will be difficult to trace their whereabouts from there with my connections.[l][r]
Based on her behavior and belongings from her time in Tokyo, we can surmise that Chito had no other identifiable friends besides Yuri, and that Yuri had severed all of his social ties at some point.[l][r]
[r]Some information and speculation has been obtained about his whereabouts from Hong Kong. It is possible that he passed through Central Asia and headed overland toward Eastern Europe or Russia.[l][r]
Russia... Yuri must have selected Russian. [r]
Could it be for just this moment...? [l][r]
No, you're probably overthinking it. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

